      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) equipped with the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six and a proper 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS refresh and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term reliability of the valvetrain and bottom end. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate the common floor-pan fatigue issues inherent to this chassis. Suspension kinematics are sharpened via fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows honest wear typical of a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust with exceptional compression and a linear power delivery to the limited-slip differential. A performance-first example for the discerning enthusiast.",
